Question: Find all airlines that have flights from airport 'CVO' but not from 'APG'.
Query Gold: SELECT T1.Airline FROM AIRLINES AS T1 JOIN FLIGHTS AS T2 ON T1.uid  =  T2.Airline WHERE T2.SourceAirport  =  "CVO" EXCEPT SELECT T1.Airline FROM AIRLINES AS T1 JOIN FLIGHTS AS T2 ON T1.uid  =  T2.Airline WHERE T2.SourceAirport  =  "APG"
Query Generated: SELECT DISTINCT airlines.airline, airlines.abbreviation FROM airlines JOIN flights ON airlines.airline = flights.airline WHERE flights.sourceairport = 'CVO' AND flights.airline NOT IN (     SELECT DISTINCT flights.airline     FROM flights     WHERE flights.sourceairport = 'APG' )
Most Frequent Query: SELECT DISTINCT airlines.airline, airlines.abbreviation FROM airlines JOIN flights ON airlines.airline = flights.airline WHERE flights.sourceairport = 'CVO' AND flights.airline NOT IN (     SELECT DISTINCT flights.airline     FROM flights     WHERE flights.sourceairport = 'APG' )

Question: Find the owner id and zip code of the owner who spent the most money in total for his or her dogs.
Query Gold: SELECT T1.owner_id ,  T1.zip_code FROM Owners AS T1 JOIN Dogs AS T2 ON T1.owner_id  =  T2.owner_id JOIN Treatments AS T3 ON T2.dog_id  =  T3.dog_id GROUP BY T1.owner_id ORDER BY sum(T3.cost_of_treatment) DESC LIMIT 1
Query Generated: SELECT owners.owner_id, owners.zip_code FROM owners JOIN dogs ON owners.owner_id = dogs.owner_id JOIN treatments ON dogs.dog_id = treatments.dog_id GROUP BY owners.owner_id ORDER BY SUM(treatments.cost_of_treatment) DESC LIMIT 1
Most Frequent Query: SELECT owners.owner_id, owners.zip_code FROM owners JOIN dogs ON owners.owner_id = dogs.owner_id JOIN treatments ON dogs.dog_id = treatments.dog_id GROUP BY owners.owner_id ORDER BY SUM(treatments.cost_of_treatment) DESC LIMIT 1

Question: What are the different models created by either the car maker General Motors or weighed more than 3500?
Query Gold: SELECT DISTINCT T2.Model FROM CAR_NAMES AS T1 JOIN MODEL_LIST AS T2 ON T1.Model  =  T2.Model JOIN CAR_MAKERS AS T3 ON T2.Maker  =  T3.Id JOIN CARS_DATA AS T4 ON T1.MakeId  =  T4.Id WHERE T3.FullName  =  'General Motors' OR T4.weight  >  3500;
Query Generated: SELECT model_list.model, cars_data.weight, car_makers.maker FROM model_list JOIN cars_data ON model_list.modelid = cars_data.id JOIN car_makers ON model_list.maker = car_makers.id WHERE car_makers.maker = 'General Motors' AND cars_data.weight > 3500
Most Frequent Query: SELECT model_list.model, cars_data.weight, car_makers.maker FROM model_list JOIN cars_data ON model_list.modelid = cars_data.id JOIN car_makers ON model_list.maker = car_makers.id WHERE car_makers.maker = 'General Motors' AND cars_data.weight > 3500
